Invocation Name: fighter pilot trainer
des: Work out with your new drill instructor, Sergeant Alexa. Say "Alexa, open fighter pilot trainer" and ask Alexa to start your training. Get mentally and physically prepared to break the sound barrier as you fly above the clouds and down through canyons.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
